PrecisAmendments (SCHEDULE No. 23) to the EXPLOSIVES REGULATIONS which increase the fees for licences and permits, revoke the requirement to include the fees with the licence or permit application, and revoke the provision concerning the refunding of fees where an application is refused or withdrawn, as this procedure is adequately covered under the Financial Administration Act.
